The defendant Natalie Elizabeth Heideman was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Natalie Elizabeth Heideman is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.
